Exercise catalog
----------------

`frontend/assets/catalog/catalog.json` (the bundled on-device exercise catalog,
736 exercises — names, muscles, categories, and how-to instruction text) is
derived from **free-exercise-db**:

    https://github.com/yuhonas/free-exercise-db

free-exercise-db is released into the public domain under **The Unlicense**.
No attribution is required; this notice is a courtesy. Only catalog metadata and
instruction text are bundled — no exercise images ship with the app.

